  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Twins

          -  Clinical diagnosis of mild-moderate respiratory distress syndrome

          -  requiring a fraction of inspired oxigen (FiO2 ) &lt;0.40 to keep oxygen saturation of
             90%-95%

          -  a chest X-ray suggestive of early stage hyaline membrane disease, (i.e. mild
             microgranulia and air bronchogram)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  pneumothorax

          -  pneumomediastinum

          -  surgical diseases

          -  cardiac diseases

          -  intraventricular hemorrage

          -  major congenital defects
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
